OL,3,CSchool lockdown enforced for second
OL,4,Cday as 'safeguarding' measure
OL,6,FA secondary school in Powys has been
OL,7,Fplaced under lockdown for a second
OL,8,Fday, after an online threat was made
OL,9,Fon Monday 27, April.
OL,11,FBrecon High School was initially
OL,12,Fplaced under lockdown on at around
OL,13,Fmidday on Monday.
OL,15,FDyfed-Powys Police confirmed they are
OL,16,Fcontinuing their patrol at the
OL,17,Fpremises "as a safeguarding measure"
OL,18,Fwith the school remaining open as
OL,19,Fnormal to pupils.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
