OL,3,CSchool lockdown enforced for second
OL,4,Cday as 'safeguarding' measure
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Powys County
OL,7,FCouncil said: "Brecon High School
OL,8,Fimplemented a perimeter lockdown
OL,9,Ffollowing a threat that was made
OL,10,Fonline yesterday.
OL,12,F"The school is open today, with police
OL,13,Fofficers carrying out high-visibility
OL,14,Fpatrols and with additional
OL,15,Fsafeguarding measures put in place.
OL,17,F"These measures will include a
OL,18,Fperimeter lockdown (i.e., locking
OL,19,Fexternal doors) while the school day
OL,20,Fwill continue as usual inside."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
