OL,3,CSchool lockdown enforced for second
OL,4,Cday as 'safeguarding' measure
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Dyfed-Powys Police
OL,7,Fsaid that parents and pupils will now
OL,8,Fcontinue to receive information
OL,9,Fdirectly from the school via the
OL,10,Fschool's internal messaging systems.
